timing_genera..._ideal_latency(25.10)    timing_genera..._ideal_latency(25.10)

Name
       timing_generated_clocks_inherit_ideal_latency

Syntax
       timing_generated_clocks_inherit_ideal_latency

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to  true, the software makes the generated clocks to inherit
       the ideal network latency of the parent clock.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

